<br>
What do I expect from Verant for $10 a month?  Not a hell of a lot.  They do a damn good job of keeping me entertained for that $10.  That small amount of cash brings more hours of entertainment from EQ than everything described above combined.  Yes, a small percentage of people have problems that cannot be resolved without GMs and are unlucky enough not to be able to find one.  Very few truly *need* a GM to solve.  (A necro would have retrieved that stuck corpse much quicker than a GM.  Don't depend on the GMs and you'll be disappointed and stressed much less. :)  The vast majority of players get way more entertainment from their $10 than they would if they had spent it elsewhere.<br>
<br>
Don't like Legends?  Don't play it.  No one is forced to spend 4 times the cash to play on this server.  Getting angry at Verant for implementing it won't change the fact that they did; it only succeeds in raising your blood pressure. <p><B>Kaerel</b> - Gnomish Sorcerer<BR>
